Grey H2 cost wo CO2=
	SMR H2 fixed costs + SMR H2 variable costs
	~	€/kg
	~	Cost_grey = SMR CAPEX * (SMR AF + SMR OPEX) / SMR operating hours * H2 LHV
		+ (GAS PRICE/1000 * 3.6) / SMR efficiency * H2 LHV
		+ (CARBON TAX/1000) * SMR emission factor
		
		CT** = (Alt_cost - (SMR CAPEX * (SMR AF + SMR OPEX) / SMR operating hours * H2 LHV
		+ (GAS PRICE/1000 * 3.6) / SMR efficiency * H2 LHV)) / SMR emission factor \
		* 1000
