		 (1-HD scrappage value) + Vehicle insurance) / HD annual km
	~	€/km
	~		|

HD ICE CAPEX=
	(HD ICE powertrain CAPEX + HD ICE storage CAPEX + HD rest of vehicle CAPEX) * (HD AF\
		 * (1-HD scrappage value) + Vehicle insurance) / HD annual km
	~	€/km
	~		|

