international shipping hydrogen demand=
	international shipping MeOH hydrogen demand + international shipping NH3 hydrogen demand
	~	t H2
	~	Convert from GWh to GJ, then from GJ to tons fuel, then from tons fuel to tons H2.
		Example 1:
		MeOH cons. [GWh] * 3600 [GJ/GWh] / 19.9 [GJ/t] / 15.7 [t MeOH/t H2]
		Example 2:
		NH3 cons. [GWh] * 3600 [GJ/GWh] / 18.6 [GJ/t] / 5.56 [t NH3/t H2]
	|

light duty subsidy YTD= INTEG (
	IF THEN ELSE(
	  MODULO(Time, 1 ) >= TIME STEP ,
	  (Green H2 actual subsidy + LD FCEV H2 actual subsidy) * light duty hydrogen demand\
		 / 1000 ,
	  -light duty subsidy YTD / TIME STEP ),
		0)
	~	M€
	~		|

domestic shipping hydrogen demand=
	domestic shipping FC hydrogen demand + domestic shipping MeOH hydrogen demand
	~	t H2
	~	Convert from GWh to GJ, then from GJ to tons fuel, then from tons fuel to tons H2.
		Example 1:
		MeOH cons. [GWh] * 3600 [GJ/GWh] / 19.9 [GJ/t] / 15.7 [t MeOH/t H2]
		Example 2:
		NH3 cons. [GWh] * 3600 [GJ/GWh] / 18.6 [GJ/t] / 5.56 [t NH3/t H2]
	|

international aviation hydrogen demand=
