H2DRI learning curve=
	(MAX(H2DRI plant size, H2DRI EAF) / H2DRI plant size) ^ ( LN(1 - H2DRI learning rate\
		) / LN(2) )
	~	percent
	~	Needs to have built the equivalent to 2 MT/steel/year of capacity before \
		further learning is obtained.
	|

